Hello- i have a lajoie, with bat, sgc 50. The card looks like an 8. Sgc says the card has a very small paper wrinkle, but i can not find it anywhere. Even if it did exist, i can't imagine why this card did not receive a grade of 60 or even 70. I can send scans if you like. Thanks-kevin
